{"type":"message","id":"90511433","parentId":"78c49b11","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:23:36.449Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_y2yla9ldl7ya_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 3924\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='research/HYBRID_CFI_FREQ_EXPERIMENT.md' new_len=1474\n[mutation proposed] research/HYBRID_CFI_FREQ_EXPERIMENT.md\n[master 7fb18ce] pulse: 2026-03-24 142315\n 6 files changed, 193 insertions(+), 105 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 142315.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 142315.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 142214.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 142315 - The CFI Compression Experiment revealed the \"constant format problem\" - tokens like \"for next instantiation\" with freq=160 and CFI=1.00 are pure metaprogramming artifacts. The hybrid formula `score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120)` should separate these from true research tokens like \"Phase 1\" (freq=136, CFI=0.96). This experiment is ready to run.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"oceanic-lobster","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 3924\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='research/HYBRID_CFI_FREQ_EXPERIMENT.md' new_len=1474\n[mutation proposed] research/HYBRID_CFI_FREQ_EXPERIMENT.md\n[master 7fb18ce] pulse: 2026-03-24 142315\n 6 files changed, 193 insertions(+), 105 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 142315.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 142315.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 142214.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 142315 - The CFI Compression Experiment revealed the \"constant format problem\" - tokens like \"for next instantiation\" with freq=160 and CFI=1.00 are pure metaprogramming artifacts. The hybrid formula `score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, fr